            "title": "財律指揮｜受壓競爭及中東局勢 AI要找生存能力強 IBM穩打穩紮值吸｜曲鳴",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ybwf5NxWtEIXdmBWRmtX8w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/fcc03fbcecaf5cc41909c66f6895da7f\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊局勢僵持不下，又傾又打的情形未變，加上AI巨額開支能否找續下去，又能否回本都成為今年的市場焦畸，不過，IBM與燒錢博增長的雲計算公司不同，IBM 本身有強大硬件基礎與軟件系統，能在不承擔超大規模資本開支的前提下，穩健地構建與擴張下一代 AI 技術線。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">IBM穩打穩紮但不代表不思進取，近年先後收購 HashiCorp 與 Confluent，透過 IBM 的銷售網絡，推動公司 AI解決方案業務，加上在量子計算領域的長遠布局，IBM 的增長動力屬於相當多元化。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-208759dd-7a6b-310d-9239-978527781009-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年在AI kill Software的憂慮下， IBM 今年表現仍然勝過不少大型軟體同行，但目前股價相較於Mega-cap Tech仍有顯著折讓。在市場氣氛沒有之前熱烈又估唔到特朗普下一步點做，IBM穩定現金流有一定防守能力、又能受惠 AI 轉型，屬於不錯的選擇。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公司股價若回至220美元附近的水平可以考慮買入，中線先博280元，長遠則看330元至350元的水平。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E5%BE%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE-%E5%8F%97%E5%A3%93%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%AD%E6%9D%B1%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2-ai%E8%A6%81%E6%89%BE%E7%94%9F%E5%AD%98%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E5%BC%B7-ibm%E7%A9%A9%E6%89%93%E7%A9%A9%E7%B4%AE%E5%80%BC%E5%90%B8-%E6%9B%B2%E9%B3%B4-020000851.html",
